digtinfo.formcont:
Images here include: 

TotCount_UTM18N_NAD83 (GeoTiff, KMZ): Total count; 

TotCount_Contour250CPS_UTM18N_NAD83  (GeoTiff, KMZ): Total count with 250 counts/sec contours; 

TotalCount_Colorbar.png provides a colorbar key for the total count images; 

Ternary_K_U_Th_UTM18N (GeoTiff, KMZ): Ternary image showing relative values of K, eU, and eTh; 

Ternary_Key.png provides a color key for the ternary image.

The grids provided are: 
"K_UTM18N_NAD83.gxf": Corrected potassium (%); 
"eU_UTM18N_NAD83.gxf": Corrected equivalent uranium (ppm); 
"eTh_UTM18N_NAD83.gxf": Corrected equivalent thorium (ppm); 
"Total_Count_UTM18N_NAD83.gxf": Total count (counts/sec). 

Grids are in the ASCII grid exchange format (.gxf). Header information provides the grid dimensions, separation, coordinates and map projection, and z-value range information.
